  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235440/extras/2c70d23be33b9a7efbda13a78cdccf53.avif?t=1715949316\" width=615 height=86 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235440/extras/7e9d461dcb6c35b60cd4cc752e306829.poster.avif?t=1715949316\" width=600 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235440/extras/7e9d461dcb6c35b60cd4cc752e306829.webm?t=1715949316\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235440/extras/7e9d461dcb6c35b60cd4cc752e306829.mp4?t=1715949316\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Strange Magic is turning the world upside down in Equestria and it is up to you to take the power of friendship to new heights and embark on a mystery adventure for one or two ponies.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235440/extras/0069e4e60f80fb83efa6152395dc0e30.avif?t=1715949316\" width=615 height=86 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235440/extras/ab9212dce964f4c767b165e0c769c454.poster.avif?t=1715949316\" width=600 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235440/extras/ab9212dce964f4c767b165e0c769c454.webm?t=1715949316\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235440/extras/ab9212dce964f4c767b165e0c769c454.mp4?t=1715949316\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>With everypony working together, you can uncover the unstable magic that’s turning phones into pizza, breaking gravity, and splashing colors everywhere.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235440/extras/d8bcf20c29ba577d44421b66bffb0345.avif?t=1715949316\" width=615 height=86 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235440/extras/2517a42c111239d366429510f0c7926e.poster.avif?t=1715949316\" width=600 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235440/extras/2517a42c111239d366429510f0c7926e.webm?t=1715949316\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235440/extras/2517a42c111239d366429510f0c7926e.mp4?t=1715949316\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Play as Sunny, Hitch, Izzy, Pipp, Zipp, and Misty and use your special abilities to explore Zephyr Heights. It’s a gleaming city in the sky full of pegasi to meet, special collectibles to find, and photo opportunities with your favorite ponies. <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235440/extras/b595e01ee4af24af58869899f4f9059c.avif?t=1715949316\" width=615 height=86 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235440/extras/f58ce4a283464f1309744eff82cb62a8.poster.avif?t=1715949316\" width=600 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235440/extras/f58ce4a283464f1309744eff82cb62a8.webm?t=1715949316\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235440/extras/f58ce4a283464f1309744eff82cb62a8.mp4?t=1715949316\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You’ll also have a ton of fun with your pony besties, with hilarious minigames like Pipp’s Photo Shoot, Hitch is on the trail, and Sunny’s Smoothie Delivery, plus a closet full of accessories to show off your own personal style.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235440/extras/7940918a12a6d372aba1bba445b59a78.avif?t=1715949316\" width=615 height=86 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235440/extras/e524a5a230a89a344eb440fa5fcb0dad.poster.avif?t=1715949316\" width=600 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235440/extras/e524a5a230a89a344eb440fa5fcb0dad.webm?t=1715949316\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235440/extras/e524a5a230a89a344eb440fa5fcb0dad.mp4?t=1715949316\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>With minigames, collectibles, photos, and more!<br><br>It’s time to bring order back to Zephyr Heights!<br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>EVERYPONY IS HERE –</strong> Play with your favorite ponies.<br></li><li><strong>EXPLORE THE KINGDOM –</strong> Save the cloud city of Zephyr Heights.<br></li><li><strong>PLAY CO-OP –</strong> Adventure with one or two players.<br></li><li><strong>LOOK YOUR BEST –</strong> Style your pony friends with custom accessories.<br></li><li><strong>FIND FUN EVERYWHERE –</strong> With minigames, collectibles, photos, and more!</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235440/extras/2c70d23be33b9a7efbda13a78cdccf53.avif?t=1715949316\" width=615 height=86 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235440/extras/7e9d461dcb6c35b60cd4cc752e306829.poster.avif?t=1715949316\" width=600 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235440/extras/7e9d461dcb6c35b60cd4cc752e306829.webm?t=1715949316\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235440/extras/7e9d461dcb6c35b60cd4cc752e306829.mp4?t=1715949316\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Strange Magic is turning the world upside down in Equestria and it is up to you to take the power of friendship to new heights and embark on a mystery adventure for one or two ponies.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235440/extras/0069e4e60f80fb83efa6152395dc0e30.avif?t=1715949316\" width=615 height=86 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235440/extras/ab9212dce964f4c767b165e0c769c454.poster.avif?t=1715949316\" width=600 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235440/extras/ab9212dce964f4c767b165e0c769c454.webm?t=1715949316\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235440/extras/ab9212dce964f4c767b165e0c769c454.mp4?t=1715949316\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>With everypony working together, you can uncover the unstable magic that’s t