15949316\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You’ll also have a ton of fun with your pony besties, with hilarious minigames like Pipp’s Photo Shoot, Hitch is on the trail, and Sunny’s Smoothie Delivery, plus a closet full of accessories to show off your own personal style.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235440/extras/7940918a12a6d372aba1bba445b59a78.avif?t=1715949316\" width=615 height=86 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235440/extras/e524a5a230a89a344eb440fa5fcb0dad.poster.avif?t=1715949316\" width=600 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235440/extras/e524a5a230a89a344eb440fa5fcb0dad.webm?t=1715949316\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235440/extras/e524a5a230a89a344eb440fa5fcb0dad.mp4?t=1715949316\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>With minigames, collectibles, photos, and more!<br><br>It’s time to bring order back to Zephyr Heights!<br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>EVERYPONY IS HERE –</strong> Play with your favorite ponies.<br></li><li><strong>EXPLORE THE KINGDOM –</strong> Save the cloud city of Zephyr Heights.<br></li><li><strong>PLAY CO-OP –</strong> Adventure with one or two players.<br></li><li><strong>LOOK YOUR BEST –</strong> Style your pony friends with custom accessories.<br></li><li><strong>FIND FUN EVERYWHERE –</strong> With minigames, collectibles, photos, and more!</li></ul>",
